Simple example how to use java security with custom policy to sandbox plugins.

1.Run mvn package
2.Copy jars from SecurityTestApp/target and SecurityTestPlugin/target to the folder where this readme is.
3.Run testallow.sh or testdeny.sh and watch the console.

